<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Diagnóstico de motor (Check Engine)</p>
</div>
<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/50 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 ring-1 ring-inset ring-yellow-600/20">Media</span>
</div>
</div>
